name: auto_click
description: Provide several Ruby methods for simulating mouse click, cursor movement and keystrokes in Windows.                       This gem use DL library and SendInput method so there is no dependency on FFI, AutoIt or Win32-api.               (More control over mouse movement such as speed or locus will be implemented in future releases)
